<HEADLINE>
<P>
'ABORTION AND THE COURT' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I was astonished by the content of an interview with Atty. Gen. Dick Thornburgh 
on Jan. 22 when he was asked why, when a majority of Americans support the 
right of women to terminate pregnancy, the government is recommending 
overturning Roe vs. Wade. He responded that ordinarily the government would be 
