ASSOCIATION; INTERSTATE BANKING; MYLOD, ROBERT J 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA013089-0096 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 12054 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 30, 1989, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
